author: ian_dickinson
msg: fixed a bug reported by Michele Orlando - duplicate results when performing
an RDQL query (and liststatements). Fixed by altering DIGInfGRaph's implementation
of findWithContinuation *not* to call the continuation, since this was just
duplication of previously done work (and results)
